response.original_title: I Love Toy Trains: Ticket to Ride
response.overview: See vintage diesels on parade at the Illinois Railway Museum. Visit Taltree, a fascinating two-acre garden railway exhibit that combines railroad history with exciting train aciton. Great mix of real and toy train action, plus new songs by James Coffey. Guaranteed fun for the entire family.
